msgctxt "Addon Summary"
msgid "NEC - PC Engine SuperGrafx (Beetle SuperGrafx)"
msgstr "NEC — PC Engine SuperGrafx (Beetle SuperGrafx)"

msgctxt "Addon Description"
msgid "Beetle SuperGrafx is a PC Engine emulator. It was ported from Mednafen PCE Fast to libretro."
msgstr "Beetle SuperGrafx — это эмулятор PC Engine. Он был перенесён с Mednafen PCE Fast на libretro."

